WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:03.137
Hey, good morning family! I'm excited to be with y'all again today.

00:00:03.138 --> 00:00:10.432
I'm going to do another 'pray with me'video to motivate yourself to pray.

00:00:10.433 --> 00:00:27.291
I started doing these videos because one of the main missions of why God put me on YouTube and what He told me to do was come on here and pray about the end times, Israel, and where we are in the end times.

00:00:27.293 --> 00:00:39.834
We can pray together in the spirit. I do it alongside another audience because it doesn't make it so awkward for me, just praying by myself on a camera like this.

00:00:39.835 --> 00:00:49.047
This is with sister Billie Brim and with Lynne Hammond, and there are a lot of great prayer warriors that we're going to pray with today.

00:00:49.048 --> 00:01:08.591
It's just been on my heart; I told you all almost a year ago about one of the visions that the Lord showed me about Putin and the escalation of the war, and that this would not just stop with Ukraine.

00:01:08.592 --> 00:01:21.423
The Lord warned me that there would be a strike against Poland and that this would be one of the main things that escalate into World War III through Europe.

00:01:21.424 --> 00:01:30.276
Russia would use a weapon that's never been used before on Poland.

00:01:30.278 --> 00:01:38.155
I asked the Lord because I thought it was nuclear, and the Lord told me, 'This is not a nuclear weapon; this is a weapon that's never been used before.'It was massive, and it hit near Warsaw.

00:01:38.156 --> 00:02:03.005
It was a big city with a 'W'I saw in the spirit, but I have an urgency in my spirit that is trying to speed up.

00:02:03.006 --> 00:02:18.093
I believe we're going to see wars and rumors of wars. A lot of people wanted to know more about what I saw regarding DNA codes and the virus.

00:02:18.094 --> 00:02:25.485
They're asking if the medicine is bad. No, I want everybody to understand what I'm trying to say here.

00:02:25.486 --> 00:02:32.838
Like I said, I'm not coming on here to preach fear; I'm telling you what I see when I pray.

00:02:32.839 --> 00:02:51.928
The Lord gives me these things so we can either delay them, stop them altogether, or they're going to happen regardless, but He's warning me about things that are about to manifest.

00:02:51.929 --> 00:03:02.206
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I'm mandating you to get the weight off.'That was a year ago, and He speaks to me way in advance of what He believes is coming.

00:03:02.207 --> 00:03:14.518
He talks to me about the oil, crypto, and many other things, sometimes years in advance.

00:03:14.519 --> 00:03:34.446
This is another thing I really believe we're about to see regarding taking DNA with AI and creating a virus, a superbug, to eliminate obese people.

00:03:34.447 --> 00:03:40.377
It was created because the obesity rates were so astronomical.

00:03:40.378 --> 00:03:53.033
There are things I see that are very dark, and the Lord warns me about what the enemy is planning.

00:03:53.034 --> 00:04:05.194
I don't get in fear over it; I know that Jesus said no weapon formed against me would prosper.

00:04:05.195 --> 00:04:13.726
He wants us to listen to Him and be quick to obey in these last days.

00:04:13.727 --> 00:04:29.542
He may say, 'Don't go to this place,'and if you go, it could cost you your life. We need to be quick to pray and obey.

00:04:29.543 --> 00:04:48.045
I told you all I let food dominate me, and I didn't listen last year, but now the Lord is warning me to get the weight off, so I'm working on that.

00:04:48.046 --> 00:05:10.831
He will show you things to come. In that last video, I tried to comfort you all to listen to what the Spirit of the Lord is saying about the enemy's plans regarding DNA code.

00:05:10.832 --> 00:05:25.236
I saw the high blood pressure medicine and diabetic medicine, and they were using AI to make a super virus.

00:05:25.237 --> 00:05:43.874
We have authority in this earth. Revelation talks about how half of the population of the world will perish.

00:05:43.875 --> 00:05:59.467
A lot of these things are coming for the Tribulation, for Jacob's Trouble, for the seven years. I don't believe the church is going to go through that.

00:05:59.468 --> 00:06:06.157
God's not a wife-beater, and I believe we're going to be raptured out of here before all this starts.

00:06:06.158 --> 00:06:09.876
People want to know if the financial crisis is going to happen.

00:06:09.877 --> 00:06:18.419
The Lord showed me that a lot of these things will manifest after the Rapture of the church.

00:06:18.420 --> 00:06:52.839
The financial sector and all the major economic struggle will happen after millions of us are raptured out of here, which will cause a great economic crash.

00:06:52.840 --> 00:07:02.142
They will bring in that Beast system, but it didn't happen instantaneously when the Rapture took place.

00:07:02.143 --> 00:07:12.440
The chip and all those things took time to get around and get people ready for it.

00:07:12.441 --> 00:07:26.186
Last night, I was praying and the Lord told me to go on Pastor Paul Begley's channel and watch his video.

00:07:26.187 --> 00:07:44.571
I listened to Mike from Around the World and Pastor Paul Begley talking about the end times, where we are with the red heifer.

00:07:44.572 --> 00:08:02.203
It stood out to me because the prophetic word the Lord gave me was that when Passover comes, there's going to be an acceleration of things beyond what He told me about Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:08:02.204 --> 00:08:36.944
This is going to be another time of great acceleration with the economy, the war, and signs in the heavens.

00:08:36.945 --> 00:08:58.447
It sounded to me like they're wanting to sacrifice that pure red heifer on Passover.

00:08:58.447 --> 00:09:09.956
Here we are, according to what I heard Pastor Paul Begley talking about, seeing an acceleration take place at Passover.

00:09:09.957 --> 00:09:15.412
There's fruit of it; they're talking about sacrificing this red heifer now.

00:09:15.413 --> 00:09:34.994
It sounds like a big end-times event. Then we have the big American eclipse taking place on the 8th of April.

00:09:34.995 --> 00:09:42.156
It's like a snowball going down a hill, getting bigger and bigger. Jesus is coming quickly.

00:09:42.157 --> 00:10:30.215
He said, 'My Son's return for the bride is imminent.'It's time for us to get serious.

00:10:30.216 --> 00:11:14.874
I believe we're about to see Gog and Magog, the war with Russia and the hook in the mouth pulling Russia down. I'm going to play this prayer video. Let's just pray.

00:11:14.875 --> 00:11:39.129
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, we're about to see one of the greatest manifestations of the glory of God that this world has ever seen.'Supernatural healings and manifestations of the glory of God are coming before the catching away.

00:11:39.130 --> 00:11:47.199
I believe we're going to see financial breakthroughs for people.

00:11:47.200 --> 00:15:19.999
Bitcoin is already going back up to record highs. So, let's get started and pray with Sister Billie here.

00:15:20.000 --> 00:20:28.220
Father, I thank You, Lord. We take up Israel now. We pray for the military and the Mossad.

00:20:28.221 --> 00:24:51.764
All hands on that now for the operation of God. Lord, we praise You for Your angelic operation for the nations of the earth.

00:24:51.765 --> 00:25:28.244
America, you shall be saved! Spirit of darkness, loose your grip on this nation in Jesus'name.

00:25:28.245 --> 00:28:51.288
We command an outpouring of God across this land, with angelic assistance. We pray that America stays out of it.

00:28:51.289 --> 00:29:08.654
You demon spirit that has been in operation over our White House, in the name of Jesus, you loose your hold and your grip.

00:29:08.655 --> 00:34:49.632
I command the counsel of the wise to see it. We depend upon the help of the Holy Spirit.

00:34:49.633 --> 00:41:03.439
Father, things that are in Your heart, we ask You for that nation. We ask You for that possession of ours.

00:41:03.440 --> 00:41:57.679
All Your operations in the earth, the ones we see and the ones we don't, are flowing out.

00:41:57.680 --> 00:43:31.721
There is help. We're making power available through prayers lifted up.

00:43:31.722 --> 00:51:26.178
We pray for healings right now. It has been reserved for this time.

00:51:26.179 --> 00:52:36.412
Get out! It's time to go! Be free in Jesus. I want to read something that Brother Hagin wrote. These moves of the Spirit come in waves.

00:52:36.413 --> 00:53:17.470
There's another wave coming, but we have to enter into a deeper realm of prayer to give birth to what God wants to do.

00:53:17.471 --> 00:53:28.053
When you pray in tongues, you give impetus to the next move of God's Spirit before that spiritual wave is ever seen.

00:53:28.054 --> 00:53:51.220
God is calling us to pray in these last days. Before He comes, there's something He wants to do through us, His body.

00:53:51.221 --> 00:54:05.525
