00:54:05.526 --> 00:54:19.305
We've seen the healing revival, the charismatic movement, and the wave of faith, but now another wave is coming: the wave of the Holy Ghost.

00:54:19.306 --> 00:54:35.512
You've seen the power in a limited fashion, but a wave is coming that will bring His power on a higher level and in a far greater measure than we've ever seen heretofore.

00:54:35.513 --> 00:55:01.142
I can see that wave building. I'm convinced the wave that's coming will be twice as high as what we've seen in the past.

00:55:01.143 --> 00:55:58.318
Glory to God! We walk in boldness in these end times, with waves of the glory of God delivering people from satanic bondage.

00:55:58.319 --> 00:58:41.439
The European wave is coming down all throughout England and upon the nations.

00:58:41.440 --> 00:59:00.733
Father, we just thank You and give You praise. I see manifestations of the glory of God.

00:59:00.735 --> 00:59:24.996
There is a move of God the world has never seen before about to happen—a major outpouring of the Spirit right before the catching away of the church.

00:59:24.997 --> 00:59:46.791
I want you to agree with me right now that there is a major move of God happening in your house, your finances, your marriage, and your life.

00:59:46.792 --> 01:00:17.318
The 'suddenlies'are going to start to happen like popcorn in your life.

01:00:17.319 --> 01:00:50.228
Believe big in 2024. That was powerful. I'm going to do more of these.

01:00:50.229 --> 01:01:10.870
I want to encourage you all: great things are going to manifest for you and your family.

01:01:10.871 --> 01:01:40.121
Don't give up. The sky is not falling; great days are ahead. I call you healed, whole, and well.

01:01:40.122 --> 01:01:51.168
Delivered and set free by the power of the Holy Spirit. Today is a good day, and God's a good God.

01:01:51.169 --> 01:02:14.199
Thank you for joining me and praying with me. We are mighty together as a unit, praying all over the world.

01:02:14.200 --> 01:02:34.480
Put a smile on your face and a song on your heart. Jesus loves you so much. God bless you all and have a wonderful night. Bye-bye.

